				<div id="bookshelf1_left_mid">
					<div id="bookshelf1_about_us">
					    
						<img src="images/bookshelf.jpg" alt="bookshelf"/>
						<p style="font-weight:bold;">A new initiative to provide you with good books at low cost.The money gained is used to buy new books and for
						the education of poor children with ROOH</p>
						<p>We want to create an environment of sharing and  introduce a habit of reading in NIT Kurukshetra.
						Our mission is NIT Kurukshetra to read more.For this purpose we are providing book at a negligible rent. 
						Moreover the money collected through rent is used for the payment of 
						school fee of poor children.</p>
					
					</div>
