				<div id="faqs">
				    <h2 style="font-size:2em;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
					<p class="question">
						What is Bookshelf??
					</p>
					
					<p class="answer">
						It is a new initiative of sharing and reading books in NIT Kurukshetra.
					</p>
					<p class="question">
					    How can I order for a book?
					</p>
					
					<p class="answer">
						You can check the <a href="available_books.php" target="_blank">available books</a> and if the book of your interest is available
						you can order it by <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1-_FqvaNUhM0TdX-k8-jnkDVQSA1Mlg-PGN0NmGwjUOA/viewform" target="_blank">clicking here.</a>
					</p>
					<p class="question">
					    How much will it cost?
					</p>
					
					<p class="answer">
						It costs almost negligible. You will be charged Rs 20 for 10 days. You can increase the number of days with some extra charge.
						For details visit <a href="http://bookshelfnitkkr.blogspot.in/" target="_blank">Our blog.</a> 
					</p>
					<p class="question">
						What are the terms and conditions?
					</p>
					
					<p class="answer">
						You will be required to deposit a security money of Rs 100 which will be returned to you once you return the book back to us.
						
					</p>
					<p class="question">
						What will you do with the collected amount?
					</p>
					
					<p class="answer">
						We share half of the profits to owners of books and remaining half is used to purchase new books and in education of poor children.
					</p>
					<p class="question">
						I have also many books. How can I help you?
					</p>
					
					<p class="answer">
						Please give us details of books by <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1O4EwbV3MIa49QyTvpGbCvSb5XAI1pKRMWvP000b6uqA/viewform" target="_blank">clicking here.</a>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
